# Icon Usage

## Libraries

- **Lucide** (`lucide-react`) — UI icons (arrows, checks, feature glyphs).
- **Tabler** (`@tabler/icons-react`) — brand/social icons where already used (footer).

## Rules

- Pick one library per component file when possible; do not mix duplicate glyphs (e.g. two different check icons) without reason.
- Keep imports tree-shaken (named imports only).
- If an icon is reused in many files, consider a small re-export module under `src/components/marketing/icons.ts` when touching those files — not required for one-off usage.

## Avoid

- Inline SVG duplicates of icons already available in Lucide/Tabler.
- Enormous icon bundles from importing entire libraries.
